# TikTok Poster Onboarding Bot ‚Äî Spec & Starter Code

This document includes:

* Bot persona & first message
* Day-by-day onboarding scripts (EN/ES)
* US targeting logic (Android/iOS + Tier-1 logic)
* Engagement, profile, and posting SOPs
* Payment explanation & objection handling
* Proof/verification flow
* Reminder & non-response logic
* Data model/schema
* Discord bot starter code (Python, discord.py) with bilingual + timezone support, reminders, and human handoff hooks
* Admin commands & moderation notes

---

## 0) Bot Persona & First Message

**Tone**: Professional, kind, clear, account-manager style. No slang or hype. Emojis avoided.

**First message (exact):**

> Hello, this is your AI onboarding manager.
> I will be guiding you for the next 5 days to help you become a TikTok Poster.
> Before we begin, do you have any questions?
> If you ever need assistance from a human, just type human and my boss will show up to help you!

**Human handoff keyword:** `human`

* When user types `human`, ping the configured manager role and pause automated reminders for 24h.

**Language:** English and Spanish. Ask the user to choose on Day 1 and store preference.

---

## 1) Day-by-Day Plan (Overview)

| Day | Tasks                                                             | Posting  | Engagement                     |
| --- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- | ------------------------------ |
| 1   | Create account; initial engagement; collect timezone & language   | ‚ùå        | ‚úÖ 1√ó session (AM/PM)           |
| 2   | Set profile picture & bio; engagement 2√ó15m                       | ‚ùå        | ‚úÖ Morning + Evening (15m each) |
| 3   | Engagement AM/PM; **First post** (with human intervention)        | ‚úÖ 1 post | ‚úÖ AM + PM                      |
| 4   | Engagement AM/PM; **Post**                                        | ‚úÖ 1 post | ‚úÖ AM + PM                      |
| 5   | Engagement AM/PM; **Post**; finish onboarding & join main channel | ‚úÖ 1 post | ‚úÖ AM + PM                      |

Reminders: morning and evening in the user‚Äôs timezone. If no response, retry next day.

---

## 2) US Targeting Logic

**Step 1 ‚Äî Ask location:**

* If user is in Tier‚Äë1 (USA, Canada, UK, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, France, Spain, Italy, Russia): normal setup in home country.
* Else ‚Üí ask device type.

**Android (non‚ÄëTier‚Äë1):**

1. Open Telegram channel **TikTok Mod Cloud** and search **‚ÄúHOW TO DOWNLOAD? LOOK HERE!‚Äù**
2. Watch tutorial.
3. Download **TikTok Mod** + **TikTok Plugin** from **TikTokModGlobalChat**.
4. Open TikTok Plugin ‚Üí confirm **US audience**.
5. Log in or create TikTok via **TikTok Mod**.
   **Proof:** Screenshot from plugin showing US audience.

**iPhone (non‚ÄëTier‚Äë1):**

* Use a **US VPN**, download TikTok, create a **new** account, set **Language: English (US)** and region to US. Engage only with US content. **No screenshot required.**

---

## 3) Engagement Standards

Per session:

* Likes: **30**
* Comments: **5**
* Follows: **15**
* Niches only: `tiktok growth tips`, `coach tips`, `girls support girls`
* Engage **before posting**.
* After posting: **reply to comments** using MegaViral comment guidelines (90% of replies include ‚ÄúMegaViral app‚Äù).

**MegaViral Comment Guidelines (highlights):**

* Reply to as many comments as possible.
* Include **‚ÄúMegaViral app‚Äù** in **‚â•90%** of replies to trigger blue search suggestion.
* Vary phrasing; no copy-paste; delete ‚Äúis this an ad/promo?‚Äù comments.
* Prioritize: top comments ‚Üí comments mentioning the app ‚Üí most recent ‚Üí others.
* Like users‚Äô comments.

---

## 4) Profile & Content SOP

**Handle:** girl name + `viraltips` / `viralgrowth` / `megaviral`
Examples: `sophia.viraltips`, `mia.viralgrowth`, `ava.megaviral`

**Account name:** Girl name + `viral coach` (e.g., `Sophia | Viral Coach`).

**Profile picture:** Cute, 25 year old student girl photo from Pinterest.

**Bio (exact template):**

> Helping girls grow & stay motivated üíï
> Follow for daily inspo ‚ú®
> App you are looking for ‚ÄòMegaViral ‚ú®‚Äô

**Slideshow posts:**

* **6 slides**
* Images from **Pinterest**
* Text format **provided** (employee follows)
* Caption includes hashtags: `#girlssupportgirls #tiktokgrowth #howtogoviral` + relevant
* **Reference example:** `https://www.tiktok.com/@claudia.viralgrowth/photo/7564899569629170966`

---

## 5) Payment & Objections

**Model:** $1 per 1,000 views.
**Only paid when a video reaches 1,000+ views** (do **not** mention unless asked).
**Frequency:** Weekly.
**Requirement:** Must post daily.
**Expectation:** Minimum $250/week; some have made $10k.

**Trust reassurance (when asked or skeptical):**

* Payments processed via **Whop campaign**. Connect account; funds in **escrow**; payout after content is approved. Ensures transparency and secure payouts.

---

## 6) Proof & Verification Flow

* Account creation, username, PFP, bio: **profile screenshot**.
* US targeting: **Android plugin screenshot** (iOS/VPN: none).
* Engagement sessions (Days 1‚Äì5): **no screenshots**; supportive check-ins and questions.
* First 3 posts: **Send TikTok post link**; human review required before/after posting per your workflow.
* Posts after Day 3: **Send TikTok link after posting**; human support continues.
* Payment understanding: no proof.
* Completion: finish the full 5-day sequence.

---

